# 🏠 Namma Ooru Smart Solutions — Full Project Explanation

## 📌 What Is This Project?

**Namma Ooru Smart Solutions** is a **React-based business website + e-commerce frontend** for a smart home electronics & energy solutions shop based in **Udumalpet, Tamil Nadu**. It allows customers to browse products, add them to a cart, fill in their details, and receive an **auto-generated PDF invoice** — while simultaneously notifying both the shop owner and customer via **WhatsApp**.

It is a **fully frontend-only** app — no backend server, no database. It is deployed to **GitHub Pages** via `gh-pages`.

---

